text = "The Kingdom of Shadows is a highly controversial novel which some critics have deemed “gruesome” and “unreadable.” It has earned a place on many “banned books” lists due to Berlusconi’s graphic portrayals of violence, torture, and death. Although it never achieved commercial success, it has sparked a dedicated and lasting cult following that is still active in online circles today."
